{"type":"text","timestamp":1778377830000,"sessionID":"ses_1f06cb1ecffe4eQwWh340yWv8Y","part":{"id":"prt_e0f942843001qes7QHq70fpwki","messageID":"msg_e0f9415df001uSSlhhcaFtrx43","sessionID":"ses_1f06cb1ecffe4eQwWh340yWv8Y","type":"text","text":"I found the issue URL points at `UBERON:0002835`, but the current ontology shows `UBERON:0002835` is the thoracic dorsal root ganglion and its parent is `UBERON:0000961` thoracic ganglion. The actionable fix is therefore to edit both stanzas: remove the incorrect `is_a` edge from `UBERON:0002835` and rename `UBERON:0000961` to the already-present exact synonym `thoracic paravertebral ganglion`, preserving the old wording as broader lexical information.","time":{"start":1778377828419,"end":1778377829998},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_025d90e9022e3bd60169ffe4646644819192231d7f0fe0adb6","phase":"commentary"}}}}
